47\" alt=\"Wine Tour Beaver Dam Wisconsin\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/20230915_173535-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/20230915_173535-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/20230915_173535-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/20230915_173535-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/20230915_173535-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/20230915_173535-2048x2048.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-722e00e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"722e00e\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-592e45b elementor-hidden-mobile\" data-id=\"592e45b\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-1d0b958 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1d0b958\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-e8707b4\" data-id=\"e8707b4\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac15003 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ac15003\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Beaver Dam Wine Tour<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17e7c25 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"17e7c25\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"251\" data-end=\"388\">Get ready to sip, stroll, and explore during one of Downtown Beaver Dam\u2019s most anticipated events of the year \u2014 the Beaver Dam Wine Tour!<\/p><p data-start=\"390\" data-end=\"643\">Participants will enjoy an evening of wine tasting while visiting a variety of local businesses throughout downtown. It\u2019s the perfect opportunity to discover new favorites, connect with friends, and experience all that our vibrant downtown has to offer.<\/p><p data-start=\"645\" data-end=\"678\"><strong data-start=\"645\" data-end=\"676\">Your registration includes:<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"679\" data-end=\"817\"><li data-start=\"679\" data-end=\"704\"><p data-start=\"681\" data-end=\"704\">A souvenir wine glass<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"705\" data-end=\"743\"><p data-start=\"707\" data-end=\"743\">A wristband indicating you are 21+<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"744\" data-end=\"787\"><p data-start=\"746\" data-end=\"787\">Wine samples at participating locations<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"788\" data-end=\"817\"><p data-start=\"790\" data-end=\"817\">Raffle entries for prizes<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"819\" data-end=\"905\">Early bird pricing will be available for a limited time, so be sure to register early!<\/p><p data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"1019\"><strong data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"936\">Designated Driver tickets<\/strong> will also be available and include non-alcoholic refreshments at select locations.<\/p><p data-start=\"1021\" data-end=\"1207\">Whether you\u2019re a longtime wine tour fan or attending for the first time, this event offers a fun, relaxed way to support local businesses and enjoy an evening out in Downtown Beaver Dam.<\/p><p data-start=\"1209\" data-end=\"1338\">More details \u2014 including participating locations, event features, and ticket information \u2014 will be announced closer to the event.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-8f6b077\" data-id=\"8f6b077\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11d35fa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"11d35fa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Wineries &amp; wines featured at the 2025 Wine Tour, that can be purchased locally:\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f338e5e elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f338e5e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/mymarketstores.com\/beaver-dam\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/The-Market-Food-Pride-1024x1024.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-15468\" alt=\"The Market Beaver Dam Wisconsin\" srcset=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/The-Market-Food-Pride-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/The-Market-Food-Pride-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/The-Market-Food-Pride.jpg 1201w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e3b9517 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e3b9517\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\u00a0<\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.zieglerwinery.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Ziegler Winery<\/strong><\/a> | Escarpment Red &amp; White, Wiscato Red &amp; White<\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.joshcellars.com\/?srsltid=AfmBOoojwsPzV55W6Cngy-KV69EePrs7gIhxVCpF-N6CehhJQvPd9yUh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Josh Wines<\/strong><\/a> | Merlot\u00a0<\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wollersheim.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Wollersheim<\/strong><\/a> | White Riesling\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-92d7c7a elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"92d7c7a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<di