\" data-id=\"3ab35a5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2a2980f elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2a2980f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/people\/Coyote-Gas-Liquor\/100094936701484\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"455\" height=\"111\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/coyote-gas-and-liquor.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17135\" alt=\"Coyote Gas &amp; Liquor\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a72f4ee elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a72f4ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.barefootwine.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Barefoot<\/a><\/strong> | Chardonnay<\/p><p><strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/vonstiehl.com\/?gad_source=1&amp;gad_campaignid=22311545010&amp;gbraid=0AAAAAD89hNJhf5CG5A47VuadbWh8RkJKq&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjw_fnFBhB0EiwAH_MfZvNnku-An9qXdLpxzS3tcChvtPKcuUlD1cFv8P4sKwRgurS3j00OvRoCnYIQAvD_BwE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Von Stiehl<\/a><\/strong> | Crimson Royale<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9bf73e3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"9bf73e3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-968005e elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"968005e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"27\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Ellipse-1.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-2108\" alt=\"Decorative orange dot, background image\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-fa09888 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"fa09888\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-70cfba2\" data-id=\"70cfba2\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3cb1fbe elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3cb1fbe\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How It Works And <BR>How To Start<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-31766b1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"31766b1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>There are 20+ Sip Stops on the Wine Tour. Each Sip Stop will have samples available, including one &#8220;Sip Stop&#8221; being a hydration station. Alcoholic sample sizes are limited to 1 ounce. A map will be given to you to mark the designated stops. Participants pick up their glass and maps at the Beaver Dam Chamber &amp; Visitor Center and bring their glass along to participating business to sample. Attendees choose their own path along the tour and select which stops that they would like to visit.<\/p><p>To start the Wine Tour, each ticket holder must stop at the main check in location \u2013 Beaver Dam &amp; Visitor Center between 11 am \u2013 7:00 pm on the day of the event to show their ID (proof of legal drinking age) and to pick up their wristband, souvenir glass, and map.<\/p><p>No samples will be poured prior to 5:30 pm. No ID = No Wristband; No wristband = No wine.<strong> You may NOT pick up wristbands for other people.<\/strong> Wristbands will be secured at check in. No exceptions. Wristbands must be worn before leaving the Chamber during check in.\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-61a7d01 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"61a7d01\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-603af59\" data-id=\"603af59\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3aee94d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3aee94d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3><b>Timeline<\/b><\/h3><p>11 am:\u00a0 Registration opens on Friday<br \/>5:30 pm Sampling begins<br \/>8:30 pm Sampling ends<\/p><div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle\"><h3><b>Rules<\/b><\/h3><p>Must be 21+<br \/>Must provide proof of legal age at wristband check in.<br \/><strong>No wine\/beverages will be served prior to 5:30 pm.<\/strong><\/p><\/div><div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle\">Please do not ask participating businesses to over pour or give you an extra swig. It&#8217;s not worth breaking the over serving law. If you appear intoxicated, business owners and servers have the right to refuse serving you.<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-87e04d4\" data-id=\"87e04d4\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-785659f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"785659f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3><b>Tickets<\/b><\/h3><p>$45($35 Early Bird) per person.\u00a0<br \/>$10 Designated Driver Tickets (infused water and snacks)<br \/>Limited to 400 tickets. <br \/>Must be 21 to consume alcoholic beverages.<\/p><p><strong>Tickets are non-refundable.<\/strong><\/p><h3><b>Tips<\/b><\/h3><p>Bring your ID.<br \/>Wear comfortable shoes and weather-appropriate clothing, you&#8217;ll be walking outdoors between locations rain or shine.<br \/>Cross the street at crosswalks!<br \/>Post photos to Instagram and Facebook using hashtag\u00a0<a class=\"oajrlxb2 g5ia77u1 qu0x051f esr5mh6w e9989ue4 r7d6kgcz rq0escxv nhd2j8a9 nc684nl6 p7hjln8o kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x jb3vyjys rz4wbd8a qt6c0cv9 a8nywdso i1ao9s8h esuyzwwr f1sip0of lzcic4wl gpro0wi8 oo9gr5id lrazzd5p\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/hashtag\/bdwinetour?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZWL8b4Cgpdh3B6qWVNIpgm_SFAY4HrT8xvjHqFloK1MjRQ_-EOOx7C5habzj9iAhJJtxhJxDtBedoG2TX5yLxqJVebeECEd1av9q1eiN0PV0A&amp;__tn__=q\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#BDWineTour<\/a>\u00a0Event happens rain or shine. Tickets are nonrefundable.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-68325c6\" data-id=\"68325c6\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-317896f elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"317896f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle\"><h3><b>Wine Tour Stops<\/b><\/h3><p><b>Locations coming SOON!\u00a0<\/b><\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"